redirect this site "MAY 2013" WordPress Codex "Function Reference"
==================================================================

NAME
----

redirect this site - Ensure that the current site's domain is listed in the allowed redirect

SYNOPSIS
--------

Ensure that the current site's domain is listed in the allowed redirect
host list.

USAGE
-----

` <?php redirect_this_site( $deprecated ); ?> `

PARAMETERS
----------

 `$deprecated` 
:   ([*unknown\_type*](/How_to_Pass_Tag_Parameters#Unknown_type "How to Pass Tag Parameters"))
    (*optional*) no description
    Default: empty string

RETURN VALUES
-------------

 `` `(array)`{style="color:gray"} 
:   The current site's domain

SOURCE FILE
-----------

`redirect_this_site()` is located in `wp-includes/ms-functions.php`

